        "username": "spitzcor"
      },
      "date": "2014-09-02 12:56:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAh, indeed it is for master.  I was confused by the \"This patch is intended to provide a Lustre-Client 2.4.0-RC2 distro\" comment in the commit message.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
